data.name: About
data.value:
Greetings!
Tips for using this Savegame Editor: * Do the Stillsuit Mission first before editing your savedgame. * Some inputs were limited to avoid overflows and game crashes. * Do not use the maximum Spice value if you will be doing harvesting. * Do not use the maximum Charisma from the beginning of the game. * Saved games are backed up. Check for the files with a ".bak" extension. * The savegame files that you should use is DUNE37S1.SAV and DUNE37S2.SAV * Enjoy. * More tips...
Created by Stephan Fourie
